OL,3,CViral bus arsonist among four jailed
OL,4,Cover riot
OL,6,FPolice called to help were forced to
OL,7,Fretreat as they came under attack, a
OL,8,Fpatrol car was overturned and a double
OL,9,Fdecker bus was set alight as disorder
OL,10,Fcontinued for several hours.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, 1 October, Iustin Dobre,
OL,13,FMark Mitchell, Milan Zamostny and
OL,14,FCelan Valentin Palaghia all appeared
OL,15,Fat Leeds Crown Court for sentencing.
OL,17,FOpening the case, prosecutor Richard
OL,18,FHolland referred to a statement which
OL,19,Fsaid: "Deep cultural and social wounds
OL,20,Fwere caused that night."
