OL,3,CViral bus arsonist among four jailed
OL,4,Cover riot
OL,6,FReferring to the incident in which the
OL,7,Fbus was set alight he said: "It was
OL,8,Fstopped by a crowd and forced to end
OL,9,Fits route.
OL,11,F"Its drivers and passengers were
OL,12,Fforced to run away and leave the bus
OL,13,Fto the growing crowd.
OL,15,F"Bricks were thrown at the windows and
OL,16,Fmembers of the crowd began to surround
OL,17,Fit and set fire to various parts."
OL,19,FThe court heard Dobre, Mitchell and
OL,20,FZamonsty were among those responsible
OL,21,Ffor the incident involving the bus.
