OL,6,FFootage showed Dobre helping to tip
OL,7,Fover the police vehicle and later
OL,8,Fholding a lighter to the back seat of
OL,9,Fthe bus. The footage was widely shared
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,FZamonsty was seen throwing items,
OL,13,Fincluding a table, at the bus to fuel
OL,14,Fthe fire.
