OL,6,FMr Holland said: "In summary, (he was)
OL,7,Fthere for many hours, throwing
OL,8,Fmissiles at the bus, putting items
OL,9,Fonto the bus to encourage it to burn
OL,10,Fand even as the bus is a shell,
OL,11,Ffeeding the fire with many items
OL,12,Fincluding bins and a sofa."
OL,14,FMitchell was seen with a group of
OL,15,Fpeople trying to set rubbish alight
OL,16,Fand throwing it at the bus.
OL,18,FIn a statement First bus company said
OL,19,Fstaff had suffered an immeasurable
OL,20,F"psychological and emotional impact".
