OL,6,FIt said: "We have supported our
OL,7,Fdriver, but this incident certainly
OL,8,Fhad an impact on him and he has
OL,9,Fremained off work... It is a
OL,10,Fpossibility he may not return and we
OL,11,Fmay lose him as a result.
OL,13,F"The team spent many weeks afterwards
OL,14,Fsupporting drivers who expressed
OL,15,Fconcerns about driving these routes."
OL,17,FPalaghia was not involved in setting
OL,18,Fthe bus alight but was involved in
OL,19,Fstarting another fire.
