OL,6,FThe court heard the cost of policing
OL,7,Fthe violence was an estimated
OL,8,F#276,000, on top of the cost of
OL,9,Frepairing damaged vehicles.
OL,11,FThe cost to the bus company was
OL,12,Festimated at #500,000.
OL,14,FNone of the four men were involved
OL,15,Fwith the family at the centre of the
OL,16,Finitial child protection matter.
