OL,6,FMitchell, 34, of Strathmore View, and
OL,7,FMilan Zamostny, 30, of Luxor Avenue,
OL,8,Fboth pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,9,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,10,Fendangered and violent disorder.
OL,11,FMitchell received a six-year sentence.
OL,12,FZamostny was jailed for five years and
OL,13,Ffour months.
OL,15,FPalaghia, 21, admitted violent
OL,16,Fdisorder and arson. He was jailed for
OL,17,Fthree years.
OL,19,FForty-one people have so far been
OL,20,Farrested following the incident in
OL,21,FHarehills.
