OL,6,FCh Supt Steve Dodds, Leeds police
OL,7,Fcommander, said: "The disorder which
OL,8,Ftook place in Harehills earlier this
OL,9,Fsummer was shameful. It saw these men
OL,10,Fand others engage in disgraceful acts
OL,11,Fwhich harmed the very communities in
OL,12,Fwhich they lived."
